
@COM1000
;母乳分泌促進薬

SELECTCOM = 1000
LOSEBASE:体力 += 30
LOSEBASE:気力 += 30
SOURCE:Ｎ痛み = 1000
SOURCE:恥辱 = 1000
SOURCE:屈辱 = 1000
SOURCE:支配 = 600
SOURCE:経過時間 = 1
SOURCE:選択コマンド口上非表示 = 1
EXP:肉体改造 ++
SETBIT ＃有効薬品／母乳分泌促進薬＃
ITEM:母乳分泌促進薬 --
CALL BUST_TENTACLE_RESET
TRYCALLFORM COM{SELECTCOM}_MESSAGE
RETURN 1



